			<h3 id="logo">
			  <li><strong>Upload Logo</strong>- <a href="#toc">top</a></li></h3>
			<p>Access your blog <b>Layout </b>&gt; click <b>Edit </b>link on <b>Header </b>widget<br />
			</p>
			<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
			<img border="0" src="assets/images/logo.png" /></div>
		  In <b>Configure Header</b> window, input you <strong>Blog Title</strong> and <strong>Blog Description</strong>. If you want to upload your image logo, make sure checked <strong class="highlight">Instead of title and description</strong>, then click <strong>Choose File</strong> and locate your logo file. And click <b>Save </b>button to finish.<br />
			<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
			<img border="0" src="assets/images/logo-2.png" /></div>
			<br />
			
			
